[
  {
    "id": "20250422-01",
    "segments": [
      {
        "start_time": "0:01",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "What?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:02",
        "end_time": "0:02",
        "text": "No!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:03",
        "end_time": "0:04",
        "text": "Yes way!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:04",
        "end_time": "0:05",
        "text": "It's time for..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:05",
        "end_time": "0:06",
        "text": "News for kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:07",
        "end_time": "0:08",
        "text": "News for kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:08",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:09",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:09",
        "end_time": "0:10",
        "text": "真的假的?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:11",
        "end_time": "0:12",
        "text": "原來..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:12",
        "end_time": "0:13",
        "text": "原來..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:13",
        "end_time": "0:14",
        "text": "不止..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:14",
        "end_time": "0:16",
        "text": "你不知道的趣味新鮮事"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:16",
        "end_time": "0:17",
        "text": "ICRT's..."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:17",
        "end_time": "0:18",
        "text": "News for kids!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:20",
        "end_time": "0:22",
        "text": "To keep water in a river,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:22",
        "end_time": "0:24",
        "text": "people build walls."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:25",
        "end_time": "0:28",
        "text": "These walls are called dams."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:28",
        "end_time": "0:32",
        "text": "Dams can also keep water out of rivers."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:32",
        "end_time": "0:34",
        "text": "人們建築水壩"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:34",
        "end_time": "0:36",
        "text": "來控制河流的水位"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:36",
        "end_time": "0:39",
        "text": "水壩就像一道牆"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:39",
        "end_time": "0:41",
        "text": "把河水擋住"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:41",
        "end_time": "0:45",
        "text": "有時候水壩的功能是讓雨水不要進入河流"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:45",
        "end_time": "0:47",
        "text": "河流需要一座河流"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:47",
        "end_time": "0:50",
        "text": "河流的污漬進入了河流"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:50",
        "end_time": "0:54",
        "text": "河流附近的土地太乾了"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:54",
        "end_time": "0:57",
        "text": "人們計劃在河流上建立河流"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "0:57",
        "end_time": "1:01",
        "text": "他們計劃把乾土地弄濕"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:01",
        "end_time": "1:07",
        "text": "那種土地叫做泥土"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:07",
        "end_time": "1:10",
        "text": "很多動物都居住在泥土"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:25",
        "end_time": "1:30",
        "text": "但是,人們沒有錢去泥土"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:30",
        "end_time": "1:35",
        "text": "In Taiwan's money, they needed 43 million dollars."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:36",
        "end_time": "1:38",
        "text": "Seven years passed."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:39",
        "end_time": "1:44",
        "text": "水壩是昂贵的工程,需要台币四千三百万元。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:44",
        "end_time": "1:48",
        "text": "所以,过了七年,水壩都还没盖。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:48",
        "end_time": "1:52",
        "text": "But one day, they were surprised."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:52",
        "end_time": "1:54",
        "text": "They saw dams."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "1:55",
        "end_time": "1:58",
        "text": "The dams are where the people wanted to build."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:08",
        "end_time": "2:20",
        "text": "但有一天,水壩自己神奇出现了,它把脏水挡住,还创造了湿地,湿地比人们想象的更大,更好!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:25",
        "end_time": "2:28",
        "text": "但有一天,水壩自己神奇出现了,它把脏水挡住,还创造了湿地,湿地比人们想象的更大,更好!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:28",
        "end_time": "2:31",
        "text": "They built the dams in a few days,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:32",
        "end_time": "2:35",
        "text": "and they saved the people lots of money."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:36",
        "end_time": "2:44",
        "text": "河里就是神秘的水壩工人,他们用石头、泥土和木头盖出水壩。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:44",
        "end_time": "2:46",
        "text": "最棒的是不用钱。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:46",
        "end_time": "2:48",
        "text": "The people are happy."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:48",
        "end_time": "2:50",
        "text": "The river is cleaner."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:51",
        "end_time": "2:53",
        "text": "Many animals live in the wetlands."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:54",
        "end_time": "2:55",
        "text": "Great job, beavers!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "2:55",
        "end_time": "3:02",
        "text": "合理,天生就会在河流里建筑水壩,作为自己的家。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:02",
        "end_time": "3:04",
        "text": "Wetland,湿地。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:04",
        "end_time": "3:07",
        "text": "I'm going to 敖古Wetland tomorrow."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:07",
        "end_time": "3:09",
        "text": "我明天要去敖古湿地。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:10",
        "end_time": "3:11",
        "text": "To see the birds?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:11",
        "end_time": "3:12",
        "text": "去赏鸟吗?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:12",
        "end_time": "3:15",
        "text": "Yeah, and take some photos too."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:16",
        "end_time": "3:17",
        "text": "对,也要去拍照。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:17",
        "end_time": "3:20",
        "text": "Surprised, 惊讶的。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:20",
        "end_time": "3:23",
        "text": "I'm surprised that you're still doing that."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:23",
        "end_time": "3:25",
        "text": "我很惊讶你还在做那些。"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:25",
        "end_time": "3:25",
        "text": "Well,"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:26",
        "end_time": "3:27",
        "text": "birds are cute!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:28",
        "end_time": "3:29",
        "text": "鸟类很可爱啊!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:29",
        "end_time": "3:31",
        "text": "All the time 一直"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:31",
        "end_time": "3:36",
        "text": "They walk around in the water 他们在水里走来走去"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:36",
        "end_time": "3:40",
        "text": "Eating all the time 一直吃个不停"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:40",
        "end_time": "3:44",
        "text": "And you just stand there watching 而你就站在那里看"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:44",
        "end_time": "3:46",
        "text": "Yeah 对"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:46",
        "end_time": "3:48",
        "text": "Animal 动物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:48",
        "end_time": "3:53",
        "text": "Surely you have better things to do 你一定有更好的事可以做吧"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:53",
        "end_time": "3:55",
        "text": "Hey, it's nature!"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:55",
        "end_time": "3:57",
        "text": "那是大自然夜"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "3:57",
        "end_time": "4:01",
        "text": "Lots of water, blue skies, and animals"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:01",
        "end_time": "4:04",
        "text": "有大片的水,藍天,還有動物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:04",
        "end_time": "4:06",
        "text": "I just love it out there"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:06",
        "end_time": "4:08",
        "text": "我好喜歡那裡"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:08",
        "end_time": "4:09",
        "text": "請跟我讀單字"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:09",
        "end_time": "4:11",
        "text": "Wetland"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:12",
        "end_time": "4:13",
        "text": "濕地"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:13",
        "end_time": "4:14",
        "text": "Surprised"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:15",
        "end_time": "4:17",
        "text": "驚訝的"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:17",
        "end_time": "4:18",
        "text": "All the time"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:19",
        "end_time": "4:20",
        "text": "一隻"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:20",
        "end_time": "4:21",
        "text": "Animal"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:22",
        "end_time": "4:23",
        "text": "動物"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:23",
        "end_time": "4:23",
        "text": "It"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:25",
        "end_time": "4:26",
        "text": "'s quiz time"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:26",
        "end_time": "4:28",
        "text": "Question number one"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:28",
        "end_time": "4:30",
        "text": "What did the beaver dams make?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:30",
        "end_time": "4:31",
        "text": "A."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:31",
        "end_time": "4:32",
        "text": "A river"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:32",
        "end_time": "4:32",
        "text": "B."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:32",
        "end_time": "4:34",
        "text": "Dirty water"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:34",
        "end_time": "4:34",
        "text": "C."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:35",
        "end_time": "4:36",
        "text": "Wetlands"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:38",
        "end_time": "4:38",
        "text": "Q."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:39",
        "end_time": "4:39",
        "text": "2."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:40",
        "end_time": "4:44",
        "text": "What did the beavers use to build the dams?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:44",
        "end_time": "4:45",
        "text": "A."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:45",
        "end_time": "4:47",
        "text": "Money, mud and wood"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:47",
        "end_time": "4:48",
        "text": "B."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:48",
        "end_time": "4:51",
        "text": "Stones, mud and wood"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:51",
        "end_time": "4:52",
        "text": "C."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:52",
        "end_time": "4:55",
        "text": "Stones, dry land and wood"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:57",
        "end_time": "4:58",
        "text": "Q."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:58",
        "end_time": "4:58",
        "text": "3."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "4:58",
        "end_time": "5:02",
        "text": "How long did it take the beavers to build the dams?"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:02",
        "end_time": "5:03",
        "text": "A."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:03",
        "end_time": "5:04",
        "text": "A few hours"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:04",
        "end_time": "5:05",
        "text": "B."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:05",
        "end_time": "5:07",
        "text": "A few days"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:07",
        "end_time": "5:07",
        "text": "C."
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:08",
        "end_time": "5:09",
        "text": "A few months"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:10",
        "end_time": "5:13",
        "text": "The answers are all available on the ICRT website and app"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:15",
        "end_time": "5:21",
        "text": "和ICRT與教育部國民集學前教育署學英文吸收新知識"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:21",
        "end_time": "5:25",
        "text": "ICRT網站和APP讓你隨選隨聽還有文字稿喔"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:25",
        "end_time": "5:27",
        "text": "This has been News for Kids on ICRT"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:27",
        "end_time": "5:30",
        "text": "Bought to you by the K-12 Education Administration"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:30",
        "end_time": "5:31",
        "text": "Tune in for more every weekday"
      },
      {
        "start_time": "5:31",
        "end_time": "5:34",
        "text": "以及在ICRT网站和应用软件上查看过去的过程"
      }
    ]
  }
]
